@drjackson_sg1 @flughafen_wien @la_Biennale Hi there,
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Please let us know how can we assist you?
Best regards, Shawn

@Dschampa @Lufthansa_DE @lufthansa Hi, 
wir möchten uns für die Umstände bei dir entschuldigen. Zu dem haben wir dir bereits auf deine PM geantwortet. Vielen Dank für deine Geduld.  
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@sagreen1913 @HeathrowAirport Hi there, 
thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code via PM, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@Lydssss Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look. 
Best regards, Shawn

@onecent_ Hi there, 
Regarding any claims or refund request, please fill up our online form via the following link https://t.co/DlPk2wk146
Best regards, Shawn

@dnellybpd [1/2] Hi there, 
We are sorry to hear that you have to make such an experience with our colleagues via phone. 
Unfortunately, we cannot tell you exactly when you will receive a response since we are currently receiving a high volume of requests.

@amico_di_t Hi there,
Thank you for getting in touch. We have replied to your PM. Please check your inbox. Many thanks and thank you for your patience.  
Best regards, Shawn

@onecent_ Hi Penny, the correct contact is the number on your lost report, only they will be able to provide you with the current status, you may also track the status online:
https://t.co/sYsnb4S20s
Best regards, Denis
